	| Field | Value            |
	| Name  | Team green       |
	And there is a role with
	| Field                      | Value               |
	| Name                       | Anywhere Team Green |
	| Access to team             | Team green          |
	| Access to Anywhere         | true                |
	| View unpublished schedules | true                |		
